sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Routes
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Browser->>API: GET /api/users?reqType=registration
    API->>DB: User.findUnique(userId)
    DB-->>API: Existing user fields
    API-->>Browser: Pre-fill form data

    User->>Browser: Step 1: Profile (name, phone, bio)
    User->>Browser: Step 2: Farm Details (name, address, acreage)
    User->>Browser: Step 3: Crops
    User->>Browser: Step 4: Livestock
    User->>Browser: Step 5: Equipment
    User->>Browser: Step 6: Emergency Needs

    User->>Browser: Submit Registration
    par Update Profile
        Browser->>API: PUT /api/users
        API->>DB: User.update(name, phone, bio)
        DB-->>API: Updated user
    and Create Farm
        Browser->>API: POST /api/farms
        API->>DB: Farm.create(name, address, coords)
        DB-->>API: New farm
    end
    API->>DB: Crop.create(), Livestock.create(),<br/>Equipment.create(), EmergencyNeed.create()<br/>for each item entered
    DB-->>API: Sub-resources created
    API-->>Browser: 200 OK
    Browser-->>User: Redirect to /dashboard
